snippet.title: Insomnis - Launch | PS4
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP0814-CUSA25297_00-8083431598780981

Insomnis is a first-person horror game focused on solving puzzles to advance through a terrifying atmosphere.

The old Castevet mansion has just been uninhabited, many mysteries await you in the creepy walls of this old residence. Unravel the secrets of Insomnis and fight against your own destiny in a story full of intrigue and horror!
